sentences: RaaShaun Casey (born September 3, 1977), known professionally as DJ Envy, is an American disc jockey (DJ), record producer, and radio personality.
Casey graduated from Hampton University in 1999 with a degree in Business Management.

In 2003, he released his debut studio album entitled The Desert Storm Mixtape: Blok Party, Vol. 1.
